further into an unstoppable depression.

01:10:44.353 --> 01:10:46.560
Oh! Oh! Useless!

01:10:46.647 --> 01:10:48.226
Oh! Oh!

01:10:48.317 --> 01:10:52.314
But I don't want another child
like that miserable boy.

01:10:52.404 --> 01:10:55.571
He's making me worse.
I can't even look at him, I tell you.

01:10:56.442 --> 01:10:59.769
One terrible day,
his father left him in the zoo,

01:10:59.784 --> 01:11:01.869
