in the World Wide Web.

01:11:38.374 --> 01:11:40.533
Hey, man! Woo-hoo!

01:11:40.628 --> 01:11:43.379
Go, USA! Yeah, man, I'm gonna do it!

01:11:45.883 --> 01:11:47.841
